{"word":"H2947 - טֵפַח - ṭêphach - tay'-fakh - Coping","slug":"H2947","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">טֵפַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ṭêphach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>tay'-fakh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Coping"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D8;&#x05E4;&#x05D7; - t&#x0323;e&#x0302;phach</b> - <i>tay'-fakh</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H2946\">H2946</a>; a <i>spread</i> of the hand, that is, a <i>palm breadth</i> (not &ldquo;span&rdquo; of the fingers); architecturally a <i>corbel</i> (as a supporting palm): - coping, hand-breadth."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H2946\">H2946</a>, <a href=\"#/H2948\">H2948</a>, <a href=\"#/H2949\">H2949</a>, <a href=\"#/H4304\">H4304</a>"}]}